abstract: >-
  The Universal Prompt Engineering Framework v3.0 is an
  advanced, production-ready system designed to transform
  any raw prompt into an optimized, high-quality prompt
  that works seamlessly across all major AI models
  including ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Llama, DeepSeek, and
  Grok. The framework features an Effectiveness Vector
  (EV) scoring system with 8 quality metrics,
  auto-optimization capabilities, comprehensive testing
  suite, multi-language support, and built-in safety
  compliance. It provides a YAML-structured architecture
  with the Universal SuperTemplate v3.0 for creating
  production-ready prompts with minimum quality score of
  0.85/1.00.
